"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#H1731662590\">",
"      Is there anything I can do on my own to protect my heart and my health?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#H1731662597\">",
"      More on this topic",
"     </a>",
