"     <sub>",
"      2",
"     </sub>",
"     (PaCO",
"     <sub>",
"      2",
"     </sub>",
"     ) greater than 50 mmHg (6.7 kPa) while breathing ambient air at sea level.",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     From: the Global Strategy for Diagnosis, Management and Prevention of COPD 2011, Global Initiative for Chronic Obstructive Lung Disease (GOLD),",
